# 🍲 Recipe Hub  

A simple and interactive recipe website where users can explore different recipes, learn about ingredients, and connect with us via email or Instagram.  

---

## 📌 Project Purpose  
The goal of this project is to build a beginner-friendly **web application** using **HTML, CSS, and JavaScript**. It showcases skills in:  
- Structuring content with HTML  
- Styling with CSS  
- Adding interactivity with JavaScript  
- Hosting a project live on the web  

---

## 📂 Project Structure  
Recipe_Hub/
│
├── index.html # Main landing page
├── about.html # About section page
├── recipe.html 
├── nutrition.html 
├── contact.html # Contact page
│
├── styles/
│ └── styles.css # Main stylesheet
│
├── scripts/
│ └── script.js # JavaScript for interactivity
│
└── images/ # Images


---

## 🌐 Live Demo  
🔗 [View Live Project](https://kirumahsrecipehubs.netlify.app/)  

---

## 🚀 Features  
- Homepage with a clean UI for recipes  
- About section describing the purpose of Recipe Hub  
- Contact section with interactive **email** and **Instagram** links  
- Responsive design for mobile and desktop  

---

## 🛠️ Technologies Used  
- **HTML5**  
- **CSS3**  
- **JavaScript (ES6)**  
- **Netlify** (for deployment)  

